title: Nine Inch Nails - Seeds 01-08
description:
NINE INCH NAILS
SEEDS 01-08

Includes:
Seed 01 - Collected DVD rip 
Seed 02 - The Definitive NIN - The Singles
Seed 03 - The Definitive NIN - Deep Cuts
Seed 04 - The Definitive NIN - Quiet Tracks
Seed 05 - Lights In The Sky - Over North America 2008 Tour Sampler
Seed 06 - NINJA 2009 Tour Sampler
Seed 07 - Live 2013 EP
Seed 08 - Remix 2014 EP

Most of the songs, if not all should have the lyrics imbedded. So if you have an iPhone/iPod, tap the album art, and the lyrics will show up! (make sure you have lyrics and podcast info turned on in your music settings [settings: music: lyrics and podcast info on])
